'''火盆'''是一种容器，容器內放置[[木炭|木炭]]或其他[[固体燃料|固体燃料]]，點燃後可以產生火焰，可用於烹饪、取暖或各種文化仪式。火盆自古以来就被使用，[[尼姆鲁德|尼姆鲁德]]火盆至少可以追溯到公元前824年<ref>{{Cite web|title=The MPs Do It Again: Two More Antiquities from the Top 30 Are Back in the Iraq Museum|url=http://www.archaeological.org/pdfs/papers/J_Russell_recovery.pdf|accessdate=2014-08-10|author=Russell|date=November 2003|first=John M.|work=Archaeological Institute of America|archive-date=2018-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180322143442/https://www.archaeological.org/pdfs/papers/J_Russell_recovery.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
